snippet.title: Pump It Up Infinity (v1.10) | Full Startup & Attract Mode
snippet.description:
Official arcade build running on an Andamiro MK9 system. Footage captured with my AVerMedia Live Gamer ULTRA (GC553). See below for various hardware specs used at the time of this upload.

My Andamiro MK9 system:
▶ M/B: Gigabyte G41M-ES2L
▶ CPU: Intel® Core™2 Duo / 2.93GHz
▶ GPU: GeForce GT210 / PCIe / 512MB
▶ RAM: Crucial CT25664AA800 / 240-pin / 2GB

Original PIU Infinity drive (dead):
▶ Seagate HDD / ST3500312CS / 500GB
▶ Manufactured on Oct. 30, 2013 by Andamiro Co., LTD.

New PIU Infinity drive:
▶ SanDisk SSD Plus / SDSSDA-240G / 240GB
▶ Replacement provided by Team Infinity (2022)
